title: Soldier X (001 - 012) (2002 - 2003) (- Nem -)

Soldier X (001 - 012) (2002 - 2003)


What has Cable become after the events of CABLE #107? Find out here!  Bored stiff while covering a Sumo tournament, reporter Irene Merryweather -- Cable's old flame -- gets entangled with S.H.I.E.L.D. and delivers an important hint as to the future of the man formerly known as Cable! Oh, and it may seem like two weeks, but it's really been two years since CABLE #107! What has happened to turn him into Soldier X? The answers are revealed here!
